<doc id="1600" url="https://ne.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=1600" title="सुरक्षा">
सुरक्षा

आत्मरक्षा वा सुरक्षा (अङ्ग्रेजीमा Defense वा defence, डिफेन्स) भनेको देश र यसका जनतालाई बाह्य देश वा आतङ्कबाद बाट रक्षा गर्नु हो। To protect a country, a government forms an army, a navy, an air force and sometimes a marine corps, where people are specially trained to use weapons; together these people form a country's military. Governments spend huge sums of money every year to buy weapons and to train people to defend their countries. These trained people are called soldiers.

आत्मरक्षा वा सुरक्षा (अङ्ग्रेजीमा Defense वा defence, डिफेन्स) भनेको देश र यसका जनतालाई बाह्य देश वा आतङ्कबाद बाट रक्षा गर्नु हो। To protect a country, a government forms an army, a navy, an air force and sometimes a marine corps, where people are specially trained to use weapons; together these people form a country's military. Governments spend huge sums of money every year to buy weapons and to train people to defend their countries. These trained people are called soldiers.

आत्मरक्षा वा सुरक्षा (अङ्ग्रेजीमा Defense वा defence, डिफेन्स) भनेको देश र यसका जनतालाई बाह्य देश वा आतङ्कबाद बाट रक्षा गर्नु हो। To protect a country, a government forms an army, a navy, an air force and sometimes a marine corps, where people are specially trained to use weapons; together these people form a country's military. Governments spend huge sums of money every year to buy weapons and to train people to defend their countries. These trained people are called soldiers.

आत्मरक्षा वा सुरक्षा (अङ्ग्रेजीमा Defense वा defence, डिफेन्स) भनेको देश र यसका जनतालाई बाह्य देश वा आतङ्कबाद बाट रक्षा गर्नु हो। To protect a country, a government forms an army, a navy, an air force र sometimes a marine corps, where people are specially trained to use weapons; together these people form a country's military. Governments spend huge sums of money every year to buy weapons र to train people to defend their countries. These trained people are called soldiers.

